<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'DejaVu Sans', sans-serif; color: #111; font-size: 11px; width: 80mm; padding: 6mm 5mm; }
    .center { text-align: center; }
    .sigle { font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .sub { font-size: 10px; color: #555; }
    .title { margin-top: 6px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .code { margin: 8px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 3px; text-align: center; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; border: 1.5px solid #137a3f; color: #137a3f; padding: 1px 8px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: bold; }
    .hr { border-top: 1px dashed #999; margin: 8px 0; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    td { padding: 3px 0; vertical-align: top; font-size: 11px; }
    td.k { color: #666; }
    td.v { text-align: right; font-weight: bold; }
    .route { text-align: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin: 6px 0; }
    .note { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 9.5px; color: #444; line-height: 1.35; }
    .foot { margin-top: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 9px; color: #999; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="center">
        <div class="sigle">{{ compagnie.sigle ?? compagnie.libelle ?? 'RESERVATION' }}</div>
        {% if compagnie.libelle %}<div class="sub">{{ compagnie.libelle }}</div>{% endif %}
        {% if compagnie.contact %}<div class="sub">{{ compagnie.contact }}</div>{% endif %}
        <div class="title">BON DE RESERVATION</div>
    </div>

    <div class="code">{{ reservation.code }}</div>
    <div class="center"><span class="badge">PAYÉ</span></div>

    <div class="hr"></div>
    <div class="route">{{ reservation.montee ?? '—' }} &rarr; {{ reservation.descente ?? '—' }}</div>
    <div class="hr"></div>

    <table>
        <tr><td class="k">Passager</td><td class="v">{{ reservation.nomclient ?? '—' }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="k">Téléphone</td><td class="v">{{ reservation.contactclient ?? '—' }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="k">Voyage</td><td class="v">{{ reservation.codevoyage ?? '—' }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="k">Départ prévu</td><td class="v">{{ reservation.datedepartprevue ? reservation.datedepartprevue|date('d/m/Y H:i') : '—' }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td class="k">Montant payé</td><td class="v">{{ reservation.montant ? (reservation.montant|number_format(0, ',', ' ')) ~ ' FCFA' : '—' }}</td></tr>
    </table>

    <div class="hr"></div>
    <div class="note">
        Présentez ce bon (code <strong>{{ reservation.code }}</strong>) à la gare de départ pour retirer votre billet
        et obtenir un siège. Le retrait doit se faire avant l'heure limite indiquée par la compagnie, sans quoi la place
        est libérée (non remboursable).
    </div>
    <div class="foot">Bon généré le {{ 'now'|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</div>
</body>
</html>
